reviewtext: This item failed after one month of use.There seem to be two breakers in this item:The first one is tied to the "reset" button. This circuit is closest to the shared socket side.The second one is tied to the "on/off switch". This circuit is closest to the wall side.The on/off switch is still lit up.However, none of the devices are getting power. The Reset button is useless and does not work.This item will be returned.
